      "title": "Discrete-time models for communication systems including ATM",
      "abstract": "Preface. 1: Independent Arrivals. 1.1 Discrete-Time Models and Applications. 1.2 Analysis of the GI-G-1 Model. 2: Scheduling Disciplines. 2.1 Single-Class Systems. 2.2 Multi-Class System. 2.3 Priority Disciplines. 2.4 Cyclic Services. 3: More Complicated Models. 3.1 Non-Independent Arrivals. 3.2 Server Interruptions. 4: Applications to ATM. 4.1 ATM Switching Elements and Networks. 4.2 ATM Multiplexer Models. Index."
